Read in the results

# define where the cache is located
db <- DBI::dbConnect(RSQLite::SQLite(), here::here("drake", "drake-cache.sqlite"))
cache <- storr::storr_dbi("datatable", "keystable", db)

lda_results <- readd(lda_results, cache = cache)
